:makestuff:__First MCE build challenge__
:rainboak:What's more fun than building an amazing Tree House? In this build challenge, we're looking for you to build your very best Tree House that will keep us safe from the rain, spiders, and creepers of course. Get to tappin' and lets see what you can build!

:stone_axe:**Treehouse Challenge Date: September 20th until October 4th**

:paper: __Guidelines:__
:earth: Must be built in Minecraft Earth
:loading: This should be a brand new build and not be something that you've already built
:stonecutter_mc_animated:  Build plate size doesn't matter & won't be a factor in judging
:animMining:Feel free to ask for advice pertaining to your build in #treehouse-challenge
:mob_of_me: All work must be done by one individual
:fast_parrot: Remember, this is for fun only
📌If it's a submission picture, please feel free to ask a moderator to pin it
